Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉液觥筹明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流民夜话诉肝肠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤魂只求歌一阙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲人不知轻袖扬

Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记不起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道这个梦已经做过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一醒来就记不起到底梦见了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你身体再好一点 我就把所有真相告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点一点地慢慢告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一口气全都告诉你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会觉得我疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在唯一可以告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们的爱比世界上任何一对男女都要深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空袭警报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在日本正在和美国交战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这边过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在被追杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回到东京了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…命…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 从前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前也发生过这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中与她一起逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比在那次更早 以及在更遥远的从前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事也一次一次地重演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我不都是知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类再也无法污染大气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命也再不会因此灭绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱依
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那个叫歌留多的家伙的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你睡着了所以对你稍微调查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的事还记得没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝军和你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了这么大亏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙不会罢休的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会遭到报复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有很多人会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是应该负下责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如来埴轮跟我们一起干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿通电了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险 差点你就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 来坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微聊会儿天也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿喝的 你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要说“从冬眠中苏醒的蛇”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我曾经有过这样的二人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说你更希望来点人血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天根本就不是个正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑蜜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能为你提供关于黑蜜的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过前提是你要加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是改主意了可以去那家画有蛇头的肉店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道的东西只能在那儿找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过难以置信啊 莱依
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你没看见酒船的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫九郎的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力气大得吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真假难辨 不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算真的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思 居座鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要是来了带到我房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从冬眠中苏醒的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找居座鱼有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又从哪儿找来的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座鱼等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把刀交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座鱼已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别难为他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎 你进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是九郎么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿的负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是保存御稜威必要的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御稜威？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能落到别人手上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要我干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来驱鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝军热衷于探求生命的奥秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了实验劫持人民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,众多的生命无辜地牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是因为血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要战友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果愿意跟我们一起并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以让你见她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密地下室？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居座鱼看来是想带他去那儿看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我们都不让看的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20年前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤帝军在这儿挟持了黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图用她的血来制造魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们必须从他们手上夺回黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们最大的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救黑蜜的话就跟我们一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带走黑蜜的是赤帝军?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带走黑蜜的人不就是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我身边带走黑蜜的人根本不是赤帝军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来真的是你 九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们秘藏了黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的血就等同于武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不能交给敌…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再相信你们说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让我见黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的事之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像不太明白自己的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是拒绝的话就只能让你死在这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个都给我住手
